prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D illustration of a minimalist beach scene, greeting card front cover. In the foreground, a cartoon version of Lao Lao from the reference photo, wearing her blue crewneck and black pants, is playfully struggling to build a lopsided sandcastle that is comically leaning over. She has a funny, concentrated expression on her face. Standing behind her, the cartoon version of Jordan from the photo, in his brown hoodie and dark pants, is sneakily holding a giant, perfect, professionally-made sandcastle behind his back, ready to swap it with hers, with a mischievous grin. The sand is a simple beige shape, and the ocean is represented by clean, soft blue and white wavy lines in the background. A single, simple cartoon seagull wearing a tiny birthday party hat flies overhead. The background is a clean off-white. In the center, below the characters, the phrase "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" is written in a beautiful, readable, dark blue handwritten cursive script.
